  "text": "In other words at that time there were hills overlooking these lines? I am Ra. This will be the final full question of this session. The entire smoothness, as you see this area now, was built up in many places in hills. The time/space continuum has proceeded with wind and weather, as you would say, to erode to a great extent both the somewhat formidable structures of earth designed at that time and the nature of the surrounding countryside.",
